data.description: Discover the epitome of modern comfort in this exquisite 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom detached townhome in the serene Woodbury, MN neighborhood. The gas-lit fireplace creates a cozy ambiance, while recessed lighting adds a touch of elegance. With 4 bedrooms upstairs and the main living area on the ground floor, this home offers a spacious layout ideal for family living. The basement features a family room for additional relaxation, and a charming loft on the second floor provides extra space for creativity or solitude. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this property is conveniently located near shops and amenities, making it the perfect place to call home.
